00:02:00.799 --> 00:02:05.240
Again, I nominate platypus for most weird
animal ever.

00:02:05.240 --> 00:02:09.830
Macaques have food pouches too, and they're
the most biologically successful primate in

00:02:09.830 --> 00:02:10.830
the old-world!

00:02:10.830 --> 00:02:15.540
Some species of these omnivorous monkeys evolved
pouches to keep food from competing monkeys.

00:02:15.540 --> 00:02:19.700
That way, these intelligent social animals
can hide food they'd rather not share.

00:02:19.700 --> 00:02:24.051
It's not that the macaques are dicks... rather
that the best food is tough to come by, so

00:02:24.051 --> 00:02:29.120
when a macaque can get a competitive advantage
to protect its find -- like cheek pouches

00:02:29.120 --> 00:02:30.780
-- it will survive longer and be healthier.

